{
  "texts": [
    "Salesbot shows you a car you think you might like.",
    "\"We have it listed at $5000, but for you I can make a special deal on it.",
    "How about $700?\"",
    "Four types of interaction were used in this source study with two independent variables: agent (human seller or robot seller) and discount (low or high).",
    "Participants then had to rate on a Likert scale whether they would buy the car."
  ]
}